      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ON THE PROWL (8) has a strong record this trip with five wins and two placings from 10 starts. Below best last time at this track (29.93) in a Special conditions H, finishing a 8 length fourth. Looks suited here and rates on top. FLEEING (4) was out of the placings last time when sixth at this track (29.87) but did record best time of the card when winning three back. Bold showing expected. MEPUNGA POWER (2) had been in great form but was out of the placings last run, finishing eighth (30.05) in a Special conditions H at this track. Generally fast into stride but was shuffled back from the tricky draw last time. Boasts two wins from two starts out of this box. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. FABRICATION (1) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
